            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科磊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KLAC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KLAC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KLAC-US</a>)截至台北時間01日01:32股價上漲69.59美元，報1452.17美元，漲幅5.03%，成交量373,889（股），盤中最高價1452.17美元、最低價1400.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.44%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+3.47%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+5.15%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>科磊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KLAC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KLAC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KLAC-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-8.53%</li> <li>近 1 月：-9.31%</li> <li>近 3 月：+11.17%</li> <li>近 6 月：+28.18%</li> <li>今年以來：+13.79%</li></ul></section></main>",
